Description: A Shiny application for the exploration of reflectance spectroscopy
    data from herbarium specimens and the prediction of leaf functional traits.
    HERBSHARE provides an Explorer module for browsing and downloading specimen
    records and spectra, and an Engine module for uploading spectra and predicting
    leaf traits such as cellulose, lignin, and leaf mass per area.
